<html>
<head>
<title>{@pre type="content" key="quiz.title"/}</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<h3>{quizName}</h3>

<p>{intro}</p>

<form>

<ul>
    <li>Create a form with name = quizId and action = submitTo</li>
    <li>Cycle throught the questions</li>
    <li>If the question has 'answerType of input', then use a textarea to get the data</li>
    <li>If the question has 'answerType of single', then use a radio input type</li>
    <li>if the question has 'answerType of multi', then use a checkbox input type</li>
    <li>NOTE: the 'name' attribute will be the same as the question id</li>
</ul>
<br />
    <input type="submit" value="Send Form" />
    <input type="reset" value="Clear Form" />
</form>
</body>
</html>
